model_specification: U_action = rho * split_self - phi * max( split_self - (token_self/(token_self+token_opp))*combined_earning , 0)
model_summary: A utility model for proposers that balances self-interest with fairness concerns. The utility is the weighted monetary gain (scaled by rho) minus a penalty (scaled by phi) applied only when the proposer allocates more than the fair share—defined by the proportion of tokens contributed relative to total tokens—of the combined earnings.
